  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BLOCKBUSTIN’ MAKES YOU FEEL GOOD!</h2><br>Embark on an epic adventure to save the kingdom of Blockbusteria from the clutches of the wicked Dark Masters!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/d479925e14f6fc24ab4b9ffe1bdf2e21.poster.avif?t=1729836023\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/d479925e14f6fc24ab4b9ffe1bdf2e21.webm?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/d479925e14f6fc24ab4b9ffe1bdf2e21.mp4?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Solve puzzles, outsmart enemies and gather gems to complete <strong>56 stages</strong> that test your wits and reflexes. <i>1 tutorial stage</i>, <i>41 regular stages</i>, <i>3 boss stages</i> (each one featuring a unique enemy type), <i>10 bonus stages</i> and <i>1 final stage</i>: the ultimate challenge for all the true <strong>Super Blockbusters</strong>!<br><br>Grid-based movement. Unlimited lives. Reset the stage with a push of a button, or return to the world map to try another stage, so you’ll never get stuck!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/0cca13bada9afed7715b267eb09b3520.poster.avif?t=1729836023\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/0cca13bada9afed7715b267eb09b3520.webm?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/0cca13bada9afed7715b267eb09b3520.mp4?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Super Blockbuster is inspired by classic puzzle games such as <strong>Adventures of Lolo</strong>, <strong>Chip’s Challenge</strong> and <strong>Kickle Cubicle</strong>. It features nostalgic aesthetics that combine chunky pixel goodness with modern gaming fun. Enjoy the catchy chiptune soundtrack by Filippo Vicarelli, composer for such hit games as <strong>Hill Climb Racing 2</strong> and <strong>Vampire Survivors</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EASY TO LEARN, HARD TO MASTER</h2><br>Collect three gems to clear a stage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/69ac98ed35d97d34d72e26c6a52ed238.poster.avif?t=1729836023\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/69ac98ed35d97d34d72e26c6a52ed238.webm?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/69ac98ed35d97d34d72e26c6a52ed238.mp4?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To get to the gems, you must first solve tricky puzzles…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/5008a8868118c5b1362345518344caeb.poster.avif?t=1729836023\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/5008a8868118c5b1362345518344caeb.webm?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/5008a8868118c5b1362345518344caeb.mp4?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>…and take on a vast cavalcade of enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/70fdbf3489c02eeade96eb0908a0b265.poster.avif?t=1729836023\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/70fdbf3489c02eeade96eb0908a0b265.webm?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2830100/extras/70fdbf3489c02eeade96eb0908a0b265.mp4?t=1729836023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every stage is a unique challenge to tackle, requiring you to rethink your strategies every step of the way. Master the game and become: <strong>Super Blockbuster</strong>!",
